    "editor.guide.tutorial-video.text":         "After watching the tutorial video below, you&#39;ll be able to easily build your site.",
    "editor.guide.menu-config.text.1":          "At the top left of the editor, using the <strong>navigation settings</strong> section, you may add/delete/change a menu's name.<br>You may also set the use of a slideshow, and reorder the blocks in your page.",
    "editor.guide.site-config.text.1":          "Using the second menu, <strong>SITE SETTINGS</strong>, at the top-left of the editor, you may change your site's name, background color, and font.",
    "editor.guide.element-config.text.1":       "When hovering over a block, you may click a <img src='https://storage.googleapis.com/i.addblock.net/config/fa_config.png' alt='' class='fa'/> button.<br>Here you may set content wrapping, the padding/background/order of, or delete the current block.",
    "editor.guide.element-config.text.note":    "Depending on the type of block, you may see different settings and icons.",
    "editor.guide.add-block.text.1":            "When you hover over the bottom of a block, a <img src='https://storage.googleapis.com/i.addblock.net/config/fa_addblock_en.png' alt='' class='fa' /> button appears.<br>After clicking this button, you will be able to add a chosen block type to your site.",
    "editor.guide.add-change-images.text.1":    "To change an image, hover over that image, and click an  <img src='https://storage.googleapis.com/i.addblock.net/config/fa_img.png' alt='' class='fa' /> icon that will appear.<br>Or you may hover over the top-right corner of a  block containing images, then click on a <img src='https://storage.googleapis.com/i.addblock.net/config/fa_config.png' alt='' class='fa'/> button to add/change images (using the block settings window).",
    "editor.guide.add-change-images.text.note": " To upload many images at once, please use the add button using the block settings window (the gear button).",
    "editor.guide.edit-text.text.1":            "To edit text, select the text you want to edit, to make a box appear. This will enable you to edit the style of the selected text.<br>Here, you may freely adjust the selected text's font, color, size, and more (including making the text into a link).",
    "editor.guide.gallery.text.1":              "We provide a variety of designs for the gallery block. You may add a gallery block to upload images.",
    "editor.guide.gallery.text.2":              "There are two types of galleries: image and project.<br>Depending on your content, you may choose a gallery type to match your content.",
    "editor.guide.gallery.text.note":           "You can choose a gallery type after uploading a first image for a gallery. After this, you may change the gallery type at any time, using the block settings window.",
    "editor.guide.preview-publish.text.1":      "When you are finished editing, you may click the <strong>PREVIEW</strong> button at the top-right of the editor to view your changes.<br>To make your site public, you may click the <strong>PUBLISH</strong> button to publish your site.<br>A published site is connected to, and may be viewed at the your chosen URL.",
    "editor.guide.preview-publish.text.note":   "If you do not click the 'PUBLISH' button after making changes, these new changes will not be applied to your public site.",

