    "board.category.cts.template.1":            "※ Please include the following information in your question for quick and accurate guidance.<br>※ To request for script application, please attach a script as a file such as text(.txt), Word document (.doc) etc.<br><br>* Site URL:<br>* Your browser (Chrome, IE11, Safari, etc.):<br><br><br><br>",
    "board.category.cts.template.2":            "※ Please include the following information in your question for quick and accurate guidance.<br>※ To request for script application, please attach a script as a file such as text(.txt), Word document (.doc) etc. <br><br>* Site URL:<br>* Your browser (Chrome, IE11, Safari, etc.):<br><br><br><br>",
    "board.category.cts.template.3":            "※ Please include the following information in your question for quick and accurate guidance.<br><br>* Site URL:<br>* Payment Date:<br>* Plan:<br><br><br><br>",
    "board.category.cts.template.4":            "※ Creatorlink offers a 7 days money back guarantee on all Premium Plans. If you request a refund after 7 days, the amount of used months and refund fees(30%) will be charged and remaining amount will be refunded.<br><br>* Site URL:<br>* Payment Date:<br>* Plan:<br>* Amount:<br>* Reason for refund request:<br><br><br><br>",
    "board.category.cts.template.5":            "※ Please include the following information for requesting the Invoice<br><br>* Site URL:<br>* Subscribed Date:<br>* Plan:<br>* Amount:<br><br>* Name:<br>* Email:<br><br><br><br>",
    "board.category.cts.template.6":            "※ Please include the following information in your question for quick and accurate guidance.<br><br>* Site URL(Creatorlink):<br>* Connected Domain URL:<br>* Your browser (Chrome, IE11, Safari, etc.):<br>* Please leave MX records information as text for mail connection.<br><br><br><br>",
    "board.category.cts.template.7":            "※ Please include the following information in your question for quick and accurate guidance.<br><br>* Site URL:<br>* Your browser (Chrome, IE11, Safari, etc.):<br>* Exact location where the error occurs(menu, block location, etc.):<br>* Please tell us with details how can we check the error:<br><span style='padding-left:9px;'></span>(If the source is modified, please tell us the location and contents of the modified source code.)<br><br><br><br>",
    "board.category.cts.template.8":            "※ Please include the following information in your question for quick and accurate guidance.<br><br><span style='font-weight: bold;'>[Site Transfer Notice]</span><br>* Site transfer is only available for sites with a premium plan.<br>* If you move the site will be moved with the plan.<br>* Automatic Renewal is not supported when you move the site, you need to make <br><span style='padding-left:9px;'></span>a new payment when you extend the plan.<br>* Please note that the Undo feature list will be initialized when you transfer the site.<br>* Please do not access to edit mode or change the setting while site transferring. <br><span style='padding-left:9px;'></span>If you access the edit mode or change the setting, the data could not be transferred <br><span style='padding-left:9px;'></span>to the destination account successfully and problems could occur.<br><br><span style='font-weight: bold;'>[Required Information]</span><br>* Site URL to transfer:<br>* Creatorlink account ID where the site moves to:<br><br><br><br>",
    "board.category.cts.template.9":            "※ Site transfer is only available for sites with a premium plan.<br>※ To request for script application, please attach a script as a file such as text(.txt), Word document (.doc) etc.<br><br>* Site URL:<br>* Your browser (Chrome, IE11, Safari, etc.):<br><br><br><br>",
    "board.category.cts.template.10":           "※ Please feel free to let us know if you have any inconveniences or needs while using Creatorlink. We will be a more convenient Creatorlink based on the information.<br><br><br><br>",
    "board.category.cts.template.11":           "※ Please feel free to contact us if you have any other questions.<br>※ To request for script application, please attach a script as a file such as text(.txt), Word document (.doc) etc.<br><br><br><br>",
    "board.category.cts.template.12":           "※ Please include the following information in your question for quick and accurate guidance.<br><br>* Site URL: <br>* Search engines (e.g., Google, Naver, Daum, etc.): <br>* Date of completion for ownership verification in webmaster tools: <br>* Have you submitted your sitemap URL in your webmaster tools?: <br><br><br><br></br>",

